    ) VALUES (21460, 'Klozepam 2 mg 20 tabs.', 'كلوزيبام 2 مجم 20 قرص', '32', '12.5', 'Anti-epileptic.benzodiazepines', 'Clonazepam', 'Sigma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '2 mg', '2', 'مهديء -- مسكن قوي -- منوم -- مضاد للصرع والتشنجات -- مهديء عصبي', 'Clonazepam is indicated as monotherapy or as an adjunct in the treatment of Lennox-Gastaut syndrome (petit mal variant), akinetic, and myoclonic seizures.[FDA Label][F3787] Furthermore, clonazepam may also be of some value in patients with absence spells (petit mal) who have failed to respond to succinimides.[FDA Label][F3787] Additionally, clonazepam is also indicated for the treatment of panic disorder, with or without agoraphobia, as defined in the DSM-V.[FDA Label]



